						               													<description>Die Legenden von Andor: Das Licht der f&amp;uuml;nften Stunde (&amp;quot;The Light of the fifth hour&amp;quot;) is a single card expansion for Legends of Andor that was released for the 5th Anniversary of Legends of Andor at the Spiel 2017 in Essen, Germany.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This Mini-Expansion can be used along any Legend of the three main games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules:&amp;#10;During setup the card is is placed with the green arrow pointing at the 5th hour of the time track.&amp;#10;The first hero who reaches the 5th hour on the time track with his/her time marker while performing the &amp;quot;fight&amp;quot; action increases his/her strength by 5 for this combat round. If several heros fight together and move their time markers on the 5th hour they still only add 5 to the group's strength.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;After the card has been used it is turned 180&amp;deg; so that the red arrow points at the 5th hour, indicating that the bonus cannot be used again until sunset. At sunrise the card is turned 180&amp;deg; again so the the green arrow points at the 5th hour. The bonus can be used again.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
